Title: Attendees react: the biggest moments from GitHub Universe Day 1 Keynote
Description:
Hear directly from developers at GitHub Universe! In this video, attendees share their reactions to the biggest announcements from the Day 1 keynote, including Agent HQ's multi-agent support, the new Mission Control dashboard, and the potential of Plan Mode. See what got the community most excited.
